Class JavaClientHelperMethods

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsb.cs56.games.client_server.v2.client.Controllers.JavaClientHelperMethods
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaClient

    public abstract class JavaClientHelperMethods
extends java.lang.Object
    This class exists to provide helper methods for handleMessage() from JavaClient to make it more readable. The two classes used to be within JavaClient were also moved here.
    Version:
    for CS56, Fall 2017
    Author:
    Hong Wang, David Roster
